Package: agriutilities
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for data analysis in agriculture  (AgriUtilities)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Johan", "Aparicio", email = "j.aparicio@cgiar.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The idea of this package is to provide some additional functions for the analysis
 of field trials in agriculture using packages such as SpATS, lme4 and ASReml-R.
